headline: Globe Life: Q1 Earnings Snapshot
summary: The McKinney, Texas-based company said it had net income of $3.01 per share. Earnings, adjusted for non-recurring costs, came to $3.07 per share. The results fell short of Wall Street expectations.

headline: GLOBE LIFE INC. REPORTS FIRST QUARTER 2025 RESULTS
summary: Globe Life Inc. (NYSE: GL) reported today that for the quarter ended March 31, 2025, net income was $3.01 per diluted common share, compared with $2.67 per diluted common share for the year-ago quarter. Net operating income was $3.07 per diluted common share, above management's expectations, compared with $2.78 per diluted common share for the year-ago quarter.
